    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. Not a single scratch or smudge anywhere\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
