    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform. The naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 features individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with rod bearings and throttle actuators proactively addressed. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M-differential lock. Finished in pristine Alpine White over Novillo leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero imperfections. A true turn-key enthusiast machine for the discerning collector.",
